{{#base headerTitle="Security Alert: Password Reset Requested" headerSubtitle="Security notification and password reset for your account"}}

<div class="greeting">
    Hello {{name}}!
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p>üîî <strong>Security Alert:</strong> We received a request to reset the password for your {{appName}} account associated with <strong>{{userEmail}}</strong>.</p>
    
    <p>This is a security notification to let you know that someone has requested a password reset for your account on <strong>{{requestTime}}</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
    <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="cta-button">Reset Password Securely</a>
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button" style="background-color: #7c2d92; margin-left: 12px;">Go to Dashboard</a>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Request Details</h4>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Email Address</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{userEmail}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Request Time</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{requestTime}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Reset Link Expires</span>
            <span class="detail-value">{{expiryHours}} hours from request</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Status</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Reset link is ready to use</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>Having trouble with the button?</strong> Copy and paste this secure link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #A855F7; font-family: monospace; background: #f8fafc; padding: 10px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 0;">{{resetLink}}</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üí° Creating a Strong Password</h4>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Length:</strong> Use at least 12 characters for maximum security</li>
        <li><strong>Complexity:</strong> Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
        <li><strong>Uniqueness:</strong> Don't reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
        <li><strong>Memorability:</strong> Consider using a passphrase with random words</li>
        <li><strong>Storage:</strong> Use a password manager for best practices</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="warning-notice">
    <p>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Important Security Notice:</strong> If you did NOT request this password reset, please take action immediately:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; color: #dc2626;">
        <li>Your current password is still secure and has not been changed</li>
        <li>Do not click any links in suspicious emails</li>
        <li>Consider changing your password as a precaution</li>
        <li>Contact our support team if you have concerns</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="error-notice">
    <p>üö® <strong>Suspicious Activity?</strong> If you believe this request was unauthorized or if you notice any other suspicious activity, please contact our security team immediately:</p>
    <div class="detail-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Security Email</span>
            <span class="detail-value"><a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;">{{supportEmail}}</a></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Report Time</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Report suspicious activity within 24 hours</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üîê Account Security Tips</h4>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><strong>Strong Passwords:</strong> Use a unique, complex password with 12+ characters</li>
        <li><strong>Two-Factor Auth:</strong> Enable 2FA for an extra layer of security</li>
        <li><strong>Regular Updates:</strong> Change passwords periodically</li>
        <li><strong>Secure Devices:</strong> Only log in from trusted devices</li>
        <li><strong>Monitor Activity:</strong> Review login notifications regularly</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p><strong>After resetting your password:</strong></p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 20px; color: #4b5563;">
        <li>You'll be redirected to sign in with your new password</li>
        <li>All other devices will be logged out automatically</li>
        <li>You'll receive a confirmation email for the password change</li>
        <li>Consider enabling two-factor authentication for added security</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h4>üìß What Happens Next?</h4>
    <p>Here's what you can expect:</p>
    <ol class="numbered-list">
        <li><strong>Secure Reset:</strong> Click the reset button above to securely reset your password</li>
        <li><strong>Password Creation:</strong> Create a strong, unique password when prompted</li>
        <li><strong>Confirmation:</strong> You'll receive a confirmation email after the password is changed</li>
        <li><strong>Auto Logout:</strong> All other devices will be logged out for security</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="message">
    <p>This notification helps protect your account by alerting you to password reset requests. We take your account security seriously and will continue to monitor for any unusual activity.</p>
</div>

<div class="success-notice">
    <p>üíö <strong>Need Help?</strong> Our support team is available 24/7 to assist with account security questions at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #15803d; font-weight: 600;">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
</div>

{{/base}} 